title: Dogs bark quietly at Christmas in Slovakia
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
Listen to the last and festive Spectacular Slovakia episode of 2019. Peter will take you on a tour of Slovak Christmas traditions with help of Viktória, Janka, Katka, Alžbetka and Marek – five students from the Lutheran Grammar School in Bratislava. Sing along to some Slovak carols featured in the podcast. Veselé Vianoce and Happy 2020! 
 
Photo: TASR
